<p>
<note n="0325001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325001">四＝五【甲】</note>
<note n="0325002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325002">以＝已【甲】</note>
<note n="0325003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325003">止＝上【甲】</note>
<note n="0325004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325004">曰＝自【甲】</note>
<note n="0325005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325005">棄＝乘【甲】</note>
<note n="0325006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325006">贍＝千【甲】</note>
<note n="0325007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325007">昧＝智【甲】</note>
<note n="0325008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325008">幼＝幻【甲】</note>
<note n="0325009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0325009">大＝太【甲】</note>
<note n="0326001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0326001">滿＝備【甲】</note>
<note n="0326002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0326002">時＝曉【甲】</note>
<note n="0326003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0326003">三＝二【甲】</note>
<note n="0327001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0327001">檛＝撾【甲】</note>
<note n="0327002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0327002">烏＝焉【甲】</note>
<note n="0327003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0327003">子＋（穆王肆意遠遊命駕八駿之乘升于崑崙之丘遂賓于西王母觴于瑤池之上西王母為王謠王和之王百年乃徂世以為登假焉列子假讀作遐遠也即升遐也）【甲】</note>
<note n="0327004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0327004">厲＝廣【甲】</note>
<note n="0327005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0327005">臼＝白【甲】</note>
<note n="0327006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0327006">迦＋（四十九年魯隱公元年孔子修魯史春秋始於此）【甲】</note>
<note n="0328001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328001">佐＝左【甲】</note>
<note n="0328002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328002">像下甲本有三百八十餘字，別附三十五卷末，cf. P. 332, b. [04]</note>
<note n="0328003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328003">多下甲本有一千二百三十餘字，別附三十五卷末，cf. P. 332, c. [05]</note>
<note n="0328004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328004">丘下甲本有百五十餘字，別附三十五卷末，cf. P. 333, c. [01]</note>
<note n="0328005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328005">弟下甲本有二百八十六字，別附三十五卷末，cf. P. 433, c. [02]</note>
<note n="0328006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328006">刃＝刀【甲】</note>
<note n="0328007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328007">家下甲本有百三十八字，別附三十五卷本，cf. P. 334, a. [01]</note>
<note n="0328008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328008">折下甲本有四百二十七字，別附三十五卷本，cf. P. 334, a. [02]</note>
<note n="0328009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328009">上＝士【甲】</note>
<note n="0328010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0328010">一＝二【甲】</note>
